tassium bicarbonate, Potassium gluconate, Calcium chloride, Zinc sulfate, Magnesium sulfate, Sodium acetate, Arginine, Sodium glycerophosphate, Zinc chloride, Tromethamine, Sodium phosphate, monobasic, More', '', 1767369485);
